That's all I'm saying.

83
00:05:45.846 --> 00:05:49.932
If the land is designated as
protected. then there could be issues.

84
00:05:49.933 --> 00:05:51.309
<i>I have it on good authority</i>

85
00:05:51.310 --> 00:05:56.105
there will be exemptions on
this protected lands bullshit.

86
00:05:56.106 --> 00:05:57.524
<i>How do you know?</i>

87
00:05:58.650 --> 00:06:03.070
How do I know? I have an app on
