88
00:06:03.071 --> 00:06:05.907
Don't be such a... What
do you call it? A <i>putz</i>.

89
00:06:05.908 --> 00:06:07.575
<i>If Mr. Bilton knows
something ab...</i>

90
00:06:07.576 --> 00:06:11.621
No. I don't wanna discuss it on
this line. or any line. or email.

91
00:06:11.622 --> 00:06:14.707
I'm gonna be back in Miami on
Friday. I can see you then.

92
00:06:14.708 --> 00:06:18.002
Look. I wouldn't be here if Bilton
didn't want this to happen. Goodbye.

93
00:06:18.003 --> 00:06:19.463
<i>I'm not back till Mon...</i>

94
00:06:20.506 --> 00:06:22.465
- Where is that?
- What?

95
00:06:22.466 --> 00:06:25.219
Outside. That doesn't
look like Russia.

96
00:06:25.928 --> 00:06:28.931
It just says. "tropical." I mean.
I'm not even sure it exists.

97
00:06:33.018 --> 00:06:36.395
Oh. shit! Look at it out there.

98
00:06:36.396 --> 00:06:37.939
It's from the forest
fire in Ozera.

99
00:06:37.940 --> 00:06:40.608
The firemen just quit over wages.
and it's burning out of control.

100
00:06:40.609 --> 00:06:44.153
750.000 acres. That is
happening right now.

101
