Well then. good
thing we're leaving.

102
00:06:46.114 --> 00:06:48.699
Is there any special song
you want me to sing tomorrow?

103
00:06:48.700 --> 00:06:52.329
Yes. One that makes people
wanna give me their money.

104
00:06:54.540 --> 00:06:56.582
{\an8}<i>Protests have erupted
in major cities</i>

105
00:06:56.583 --> 00:07:00.253
