130
00:08:44.983 --> 00:08:47.610
We need to focus on temperature.

131
00:08:47.611 --> 00:08:50.071
So where do you suggest
we tell our people to go?

132
00:08:50.072 --> 00:08:51.365
They have no water.

133
00:08:52.115 --> 00:08:54.075
I think we'd all prefer
to solve the problems

134
00:08:54.076 --> 00:08:56.577
