homes in the first place.

135
00:08:56.578 --> 00:08:57.787
Agreed.

136
00:08:57.788 --> 00:09:00.540
The goal here is
consensus on temperature.

137
00:09:00.541 --> 00:09:03.334
Keeping it below 2
degrees is critical.

138
00:09:03.335 --> 00:09:06.003
If the temperature goes up
2 degrees or 10 degrees.

139
00:09:06.004 --> 00:09:08.215
it doesn't matter if
you have no water.

140
00:09:09.091 --> 00:09:10.842
You catch more flies with honey.

141
00:09:10.843 --> 00:09:13.135
Who are you right now?

142
00:09:13.136 --> 00:09:16.265
An Algerian or a Frenchman?

143
00:09:20.769 --> 00:09:22.770
We're willing to support
certain proposals

144
00:09:22.771 --> 00:09:26.899
